13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 1792, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 1792. A. Any person who shall willfully trespass or,
17 enter, or loiter upon property containing a critical infrastructure
18 facility without permission by the owner of the property or lawful
19 occupant thereof shall, upon conviction, be guilty of a misdemeanor
20 punishable by a fine of not less more than One Thousand Dollars
21 ($1,000.00), or by imprisonment in the county jail for a term of six
22 (6) months, or by both such fine and imprisonment. If it is
23 determined the intent of the trespasser is to willfully damage,
24 destroy, vandalize, deface, tamper with equipment, or impede or
